content: No, it was made by me, and I agree it’s not quite right yet? Like I said, I feel like there’s *something* that could work with the business cat meme?
Ok fair enough. Not my intention.  I don’t like being called a poorly trained AI when something I made in good faith inadvertently didn’t land right though, you know?
I deleted it — I’m sorry it was offensive in a way that I didn’t anticipate.
